MySQL Administrator is a powerful visual administration console
that enables you to easily administer your MySQL environment and
gain significantly better visibility into how your databases are
operating. MySQL Administrator now integrates database management
and maintenance into a single, seamless environment, with a clear
and intuitive graphical user interface. By using MySQL Administrator
you will be able to:

* Achieve higher database availability through improved management

* Reduce errors through visual database administration

* Lower database administration costs through improved productivity

* Deliver a more secure environment through easier privilege
management

